Module org.nasdanika.html
Package org.nasdanika.html

Interface Markup

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Button, FieldSet, Form, HTMLElement<T>, Input, InputBase<T>, RowContainer<T>, RowContainer.Row, RowContainer.Row.Cell, Select, Select.OptionGroup, Table, Table.TableBody, Table.TableFooter, Table.TableHeader, Tag, TextArea
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HTMLElementFilter, HTMLElementImpl
    public interface Markup
    Marker interface indicating that implementer's Producer.produce() or toString() methods return markup which can be indented in the absence of text in the containing element.
    Author:
    Pavel Vlasov
